type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/group/list/region/9/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "、", "type": "text"}, {"text": "越南跟團行程", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/group/list/region/9/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "，現在還能到高雄港直接搭船去越南、菲律賓、沖繩玩！如果是想挑戰", "type": "text"}, {"text": "阿拉斯加郵輪航線", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/cruise/list/port/all/route/7/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "＆", "type": "text"}, {"text": "地中海郵輪航線", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/cruise/list/port/all/route/3/https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/cruise/list/port/all/route/3/", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "，也能報名從國外出航的", "type": "text"}, {"text": "飛航郵輪", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/package/cruise/?mainTab=fly-cruise&aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "，用最舒適、最特別的方式環遊世界🌍想找CP值高又奢華的郵輪旅行？快到", "type": "text"}, {"text": "AsiaYo", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "官網看最新會員優惠吧！", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "textAlign": "center"}, "content": [{"text": "🌼最好玩的全球旅遊就找AsiaYo🌼", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "✅ ", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"text": "如果你也在尋覓這些值得住宿體驗打卡的地方，記得來AsiaYo 下單，現在使用【", "type": "text"}, {"text": "AsiaYo APP-點我下載", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://lihi.cc/fQAiu", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "】下單有讀者專屬優惠，結帳輸入【AYFAN】現折3%，最高折抵$500！關注AsiaYo，和我們一起體驗美好，環遊世界！", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "📢為什麼訂AsiaYo郵輪行程？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "☑️1.線上下單超省心，一站式比價超齊全🌏", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"text": "全球40艘郵輪一次看，航線遍布公海、日韓、東南亞、歐美，行程超豐富！", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "☑️2. 最新優惠＆加碼好康隨時送💲", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "讀者折扣、會員優惠、限時活動超低價、多人同行免艙房費，打折最有感！", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "☑️3. 多語系真人客服即時溝通零誤差🖥️", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "台灣本土旅遊平台OTA，完整的售後服務，疑難雜症直接問，出遊好安心！", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "☑️4. 精選岸上觀光＆主題旅遊🚗", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "櫻花季、寒暑假、跨年行程通通有，包車、交通券、門票、eSIM 一次搞定！", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "高雄出發郵輪 常見問題", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "▶ 高雄郵輪從哪裡出發？怎麼搭？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "目前所有高雄出發的郵輪皆從「高雄港旅運中心（20號碼頭）」出發。可搭捷運至三多商圈站步行約18分鐘，或搭輕軌至旅運中心站（C09）步行1分鐘即可抵達。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "▶ 高雄出發的郵輪可以去哪裡？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "可搭郵輪前往日本（沖繩、石垣島、宮古島）、越南（峴港、下龍灣）、菲律賓（佬沃、長灘島、公主港、科隆島）等亞洲熱門航線。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "▶ 高雄出發有哪些推薦的郵輪品牌？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "包含", "type": "text"}, {"text": "麗星郵輪探索星號", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/journey/resort-world-one/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "、", "type": "text"}, {"text": "歌詩達莎倫娜號", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/journey/costa/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "、", "type": "text"}, {"text": "MSC地中海榮耀號", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/journey/MSC/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "，皆有從高雄出發的行程。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "▶ 想週末出遊不請假，有推薦行程嗎？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "有！像是麗星郵輪的高雄出發三天公海行程，週五出發週日回程，免請假超適合小資上班族！", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "▶ 要提前多久到高雄港報到？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "建議於出發前1.5～2.5小時抵達高雄港旅運中心，提早辦理報到、托運行李與通關手續，避免錯過登船時間。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "▶ 有高雄出發限定的AsiaYo優惠嗎？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "AsiaYo郵輪假期不訂期推出早鳥優惠、eSIM贈送、暢飲艙升等等限時專案，記得加入會員、隨時關注～", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "▶ 高雄出發郵輪行程有相關的岸上觀光或包車服務嗎？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "歡迎參考", "type": "text"}, {"text": "AsiaYo岸上觀光一日遊", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/package/cruise/?mainTab=cruise-recommend&subTab=cruise-daytour&aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "、", "type": "text"}, {"text": "沖繩港口租車", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/activity/122991/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "、或選擇包車接送，玩法超彈性。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "▶ 要去哪裡預訂高雄出發的郵輪？", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "上", "type": "text"}, {"text": "AsiaYo查詢高雄出發郵輪行程", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://asiayo.com/zh-tw/cruise/list/port/KHH/route/all/?aff_id=287&utm_source=asiayoblog&utm_medium=ayblog", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": "就能快速查詢高雄出發各大品牌航程與優惠方案，輕鬆預訂最適合自己的假期！", "type": "text"}]}]}	http://localhost:8081/uploads/cover-image/1754962296031-496749071.jpg
35	1	【韓國·濟州島】의령소바 宜寧蕎麥。美味牛肋排、蕎麥麵	<p>離開濟州島東南方的南元큰엉海岸後，我們找了在Naver Map上評價不錯且順路的「의령소바 宜寧蕎麥」城山店用餐。沒想到這頓午餐一吃就吃了快兩個小時，享受了美味的餐點，還和熱情的老闆聊得很開心，讓我們留下了深刻的印象。</p><p><br>「의령소바 宜寧蕎麥」是開放加盟的連鎖店，在韓國首爾、釜山、大邱…等地都有分店，我們這天前往的是離城山日出峰大約20分鐘車程的城山店。餐廳位在<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://www.jejuolle.org/trail_en#/road/03_A">濟州3號偶來小路</a> (溫平—表善) 上，不少走偶來小路的遊客會到這間蕎麥店用餐。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53824011807_e64c1ea824_c.jpg"><p>平日下午一點半左右抵達，已經過了用餐時間，店裡一個客人都沒有。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825168463_8fa8ee7e23_c.jpg"><p><br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53824933356_0875a1477d_c.jpg"><p><br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259549_57274a735c_c.jpg"><p><br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259644_d051280615_c.jpg"><p>地圖上畫了濟州偶來小路的路線，四周掛的是相對位置景點的風景畫。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367645_9b4b9bac57_c.jpg"><p>店裡餐點選擇不少，有冷蕎麥麵、拌蕎麥麵、冷拌蕎麥麵、溫蕎麥麵、蕎麥炸豬排、蕎麥起司炸豬排、蕎麥煎餅、蕎麥蒸餃…等蕎麥相關菜色，也有牛肉湯飯、排骨湯、燉牛肋排、辣豬腳等其他菜色。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825167883_d91596aa94_c.jpg"><p>除了櫃台上方的純文字菜單，另一側牆上則是有照片的菜單，對不懂韓文的觀光客很友善！</p><p>照片上的紅燒牛肋排 (兩人份30,000韓元)看起來很好吃，但這裡最有名的蕎麥麵也是非吃不可。老闆看我們一直猶豫不決，便提議我們點三人份的牛肋排 (40,000韓元)，蕎麥麵他招待我們吃，於是就這麼決定了。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825260169_9258a44c69_c.jpg"><p>紅燒牛肋排燉到軟嫩，非常入味。吃的時候可以先用剪刀將骨肉分離，剪到適當的大小，方便入口。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367650_756fe37d07_c.jpg"><p>可以無限續加的小菜。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53824011802_e663aac970_c.jpg"><p>主菜上桌沒多久，蕎麥麵也來了，老闆很貼心地直接給我們每人一碗小份的冷蕎麥麵。吃起來就像韓國冷麵，只是麵體換成蕎麥麵，很有嚼勁，夏天吃很清爽。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367715_461951d0e7_c.jpg"><p>冷蕎麥麵沒吃幾口，老闆又送上一份像是沙拉的紫蘇油蕎麥麵，吃起來香氣十足，我也很喜歡。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259694_50abb28756_c.jpg"><p>餐點全上齊了之後，老闆拿了韓劇中常出現的馬格利酒招待我們，喝起來甜甜的十分順口。<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259719_d3c85dabba_c.jpg"><p><br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53824012292_f693ae0fb0_c.jpg"><p>等我們酒足飯飽，吃撐了之後，老闆加碼招待我們手沖咖啡，也坐下來一起聊天。原來老闆35歲之前在首爾教書，後來母親身體不好，便搬到釜山照顧長輩，直到長輩過世才離開傷心地，搬到濟州島生活。</p><p>老闆自學了一年易經，提議幫我們其中一人占卜，看老闆解卦時認真地看筆記，超可愛的！<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367765_297c736591_c.jpg"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367775_634ede81ea_c.jpg"><p>看網路評價，老闆常會招待客人一些吃的，或是給個折扣，難怪有人說老闆開店不是為了賺錢，是交朋友來著。這天的餐點都很美味，看評價炸豬排也很多人推，下次到濟州島走偶來小路時，再來試試吧！<br></p><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259729_c198f269cc_c.jpg"><p><strong>宜寧蕎麥 城山店 의령소바 성산점</strong><br>제주 서귀포시 성산읍 삼달로 120 1층 102호&nbsp; (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://naver.me/xSckYnHi">Naver Map</a>)<br>營業時間： 9:00～15:00<br>TEL：0507-1365-7872</p>	PUBLISHED	2025-08-12 01:41:22.451	2025-08-12 09:31:06.926	2	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "離開濟州島東南方的南元큰엉海岸後，我們找了在Naver Map上評價不錯且順路的「의령소바 宜寧蕎麥」城山店用餐。沒想到這頓午餐一吃就吃了快兩個小時，享受了美味的餐點，還和熱情的老闆聊得很開心，讓我們留下了深刻的印象。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "「의령소바 宜寧蕎麥」是開放加盟的連鎖店，在韓國首爾、釜山、大邱…等地都有分店，我們這天前往的是離城山日出峰大約20分鐘車程的城山店。餐廳位在", "type": "text"}, {"text": "濟州3號偶來小路", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://www.jejuolle.org/trail_en#/road/03_A", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": " (溫平—表善) 上，不少走偶來小路的遊客會到這間蕎麥店用餐。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53824011807_e64c1ea824_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "平日下午一點半左右抵達，已經過了用餐時間，店裡一個客人都沒有。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825168463_8fa8ee7e23_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53824933356_0875a1477d_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259549_57274a735c_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259644_d051280615_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "地圖上畫了濟州偶來小路的路線，四周掛的是相對位置景點的風景畫。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367645_9b4b9bac57_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "店裡餐點選擇不少，有冷蕎麥麵、拌蕎麥麵、冷拌蕎麥麵、溫蕎麥麵、蕎麥炸豬排、蕎麥起司炸豬排、蕎麥煎餅、蕎麥蒸餃…等蕎麥相關菜色，也有牛肉湯飯、排骨湯、燉牛肋排、辣豬腳等其他菜色。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825167883_d91596aa94_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "除了櫃台上方的純文字菜單，另一側牆上則是有照片的菜單，對不懂韓文的觀光客很友善！", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "照片上的紅燒牛肋排 (兩人份30,000韓元)看起來很好吃，但這裡最有名的蕎麥麵也是非吃不可。老闆看我們一直猶豫不決，便提議我們點三人份的牛肋排 (40,000韓元)，蕎麥麵他招待我們吃，於是就這麼決定了。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825260169_9258a44c69_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "紅燒牛肋排燉到軟嫩，非常入味。吃的時候可以先用剪刀將骨肉分離，剪到適當的大小，方便入口。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367650_756fe37d07_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "可以無限續加的小菜。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53824011802_e663aac970_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "主菜上桌沒多久，蕎麥麵也來了，老闆很貼心地直接給我們每人一碗小份的冷蕎麥麵。吃起來就像韓國冷麵，只是麵體換成蕎麥麵，很有嚼勁，夏天吃很清爽。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367715_461951d0e7_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "冷蕎麥麵沒吃幾口，老闆又送上一份像是沙拉的紫蘇油蕎麥麵，吃起來香氣十足，我也很喜歡。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259694_50abb28756_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "餐點全上齊了之後，老闆拿了韓劇中常出現的馬格利酒招待我們，喝起來甜甜的十分順口。", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259719_d3c85dabba_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53824012292_f693ae0fb0_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "等我們酒足飯飽，吃撐了之後，老闆加碼招待我們手沖咖啡，也坐下來一起聊天。原來老闆35歲之前在首爾教書，後來母親身體不好，便搬到釜山照顧長輩，直到長輩過世才離開傷心地，搬到濟州島生活。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "老闆自學了一年易經，提議幫我們其中一人占卜，看老闆解卦時認真地看筆記，超可愛的！", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367765_297c736591_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825367775_634ede81ea_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "看網路評價，老闆常會招待客人一些吃的，或是給個折扣，難怪有人說老闆開店不是為了賺錢，是交朋友來著。這天的餐點都很美味，看評價炸豬排也很多人推，下次到濟州島走偶來小路時，再來試試吧！", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53825259729_c198f269cc_c.jpg", "title": null, "width": null, "height": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "宜寧蕎麥 城山店 의령소바 성산점", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "제주 서귀포시 성산읍 삼달로 120 1층 102호  (", "type": "text"}, {"text": "Naver Map", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "noopener", "href": "https://naver.me/xSckYnHi", "class": null, "target": "_blank"}}]}, {"text": ")", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "營業時間： 9:00～15:00", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "TEL：0507-1365-7872", "type": "text"}]}]}	http://localhost:8081/uploads/cover-image/1754962877153-976607586.jpg
24	1	西班牙塞維亞最道地餐廳酒吧指南/美食推薦 Where to eat in Seville, the most authentic recommendation	<img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*OU7j6jjwaq5IBl-Ee5SRKw.jpeg" alt="" width="700" height="934"><p>男友馬力歐來自西班牙塞維亞Sevilla, 我第一次來西班牙很幸運可以跟著他到處吃喝。這邊是他身為當地人拍胸脯保證的推薦，給大家去西班牙旅遊一個參考。</p><h2><strong>Bar (for tapas) 推薦酒吧（西班牙bar通常都有tapas, 可以想像成有賣酒的台灣小吃攤。若是餐廳就是比較正式會有服務生來點餐的地方）</strong></h2><ol><li><p>Cafetería-Bar Trinidad (宵夜場, 蝸牛好吃, 非常local) (招牌是豬肉片生火腿薯條三明治，記得加大蒜美乃滋）</p></li></ol><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*kKQJHYnKEXwWwJ_pSJMC_w@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*NMTOoCIh_49sBDgYwDZw3Q@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><p>Press enter or click to view image in full size</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*mDyntXuzUvJ3ZLXfsqx2-g@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><p>2. Bodega San Rafael （在市中心邊陲，但喜歡吃海鮮的人請一定要來。當地人才會去的海鮮酒吧，請點蟹腳、大蝦、小型粉紅蝦。老闆應該不會說英文，但海鮮都在櫃子裡可以直接用指的）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*nd8Vta6pmKtpxMwsIcG9Qg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*4L-9W-kVHaorgn1gJiTa9g@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*BcdaqMm7wpCUjzZUue4iXQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*dqPhxlD8YPjGrcPs9c0mWg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><p>3. Los Coloniales (市中心，推薦章魚、煎大蒜豬排配威士忌酒醬。東西好吃，氣氛比較不吵）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*B6ZMHlySLFCXYaXQp8LZtw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*cfhZ03MF3Pab8QyFDF0QqA@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*ewniT4BxBJmsj3hkubhieQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="1920"><p>4. El Rinconcillo （塞維亞最老酒吧，內裝非常好看值得去拍照。食物中規中矩，簡單吃生火腿跟起司喝杯酒就很好）（甜點菜單不錯可以多嘗試）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*p0byni__wzuHhS8JcHNJxA@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*k72ldGfKY3N_AJ6SbVcpOw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*RtttOTOFVYrmE4v1qQTW7A@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*Uk9bqtODZMZ1fBPjG-i4hw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*E88d8BOQaBbGU6Y9bnjzqg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><p>5. El Rey de los Caracoles （神秘蝸牛專賣小酒吧，裝潢簡約宗教系，只有當地阿伯會去。老闆幽默風趣）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*tP7ELrPm0y6RQMwkOk1spQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*dIfuvXvnn_P3gPd2zoeCHQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><p>6. Bar Paco Góngora （市中心，英文菜單友善，食物選擇多，但相較之下不是最好吃的）（我覺得墨魚飯不好吃，不建議點）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*a4y2uL_1aXxibFXmixALUA@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*Z6amvKg8yMxEVt1yG5P-qw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*8t5okGuZcmXRWFWaecgh1Q@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*0JwShuzEnDoAoUfsDRmsHQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>7. Bodega Santa Cruz （靠近大教堂，生意極好。草根系酒吧，有金山鵝肉的感覺。馬鈴薯沙拉好吃）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*9wwpkmuJkjzoh7zVFjVbEQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*zToNFkfzmOrh6xgXvt4USw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>*雷：Taberna Álvaro Peregil （在教堂附近那條街的食物大部分都賣觀光客，這間當地人也推薦但食物真的不好吃。酒類還是可以喝喝）</p><h2><strong>早餐</strong></h2><ol><li><p>Bodega El Picadero （老派早餐店，西班牙永和豆漿，也有賣tapas。喜歡甜咖啡的人可以點coffee bom bom, 會直接給你一瓶煉乳讓你擠到飽）</p></li></ol><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*oSXsWk3ZAweEUECJIW1m2A@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*SbjuaddVUfKOVIQdtXgP6g@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*ngqrATlKfa-wcBc2Y4a1AQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*qyDMK8bJIO54nuTTOcHniA@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>2. Bar Duque (早餐, 有圖片，有Churros,老派,市中心）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*gBvyZwlKBxyZlPnriWYD1Q@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*I-UPgaAsSzBaOUihak8TJg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><h2><strong>馬力歐老家 Montequinto (不在Seville市中心，方圓百里沒有觀光客，但食物真的比市中心好吃）</strong></h2><ol><li><p>Restaurante Burravieja （石板烤依比利豬肉片非常好吃又大盤/大蒜蛤蜊炒蝦很台超好吃啊啊啊）</p></li></ol><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*zBiehhqd7L72LfE3dLv7Ig@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*rEEDuxdXhUFGinowKpkZSw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>2. Cervecería Un Poquito (戶外座位很熱鬧很local, 賽維亞賣最多種啤酒的地方。海鮮種類選擇多，熱菜也好吃。會用麥克風唱名去拿菜）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*2z8qUV9Or39Z-mIqkQx6pg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*5PuwEMoI0Mxo47Swn5qQgw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*tXOsZORIHfXo2m0fSXPBJg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="334" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*vDuNTNEizx0fs1HJWdE3pA@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*3VBzMyRG6gnN54XWJ-6ghQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>3. Los Caminantes （海鮮極美味又便宜。langoustine(cigala) 蝦腦極讚、各種蝦類都無敵）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*G0gXCxThMBIh3CaaqegZZQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*FaGncPeODYR6Pzb9EKmZAQ@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><h2><strong>特色酒吧（沒有食物）</strong></h2><p>Bar Garlochí （極盡浮誇之宗教系酒吧，老闆非常妙。招牌調酒是“耶穌的寶血”。推薦去參觀佈置）（裡面有點非常濃的香，密閉龍山寺的概念，老闆自爆他有得肺癌）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*YhajgzzRGsUzcwDVDs1reA@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*cHu6nLFFs00pnvUFACpW3w@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*2ILiZf7JDmOzYW9eHjuWIg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*_Ifo2ju0YoPbZ2hre_1jbA@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="1920"><h2><strong>甜點</strong></h2><ol><li><p>Helados Rayas （塞維亞最有名冰淇淋店，有非常多西班牙特色口味）</p></li></ol><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*BCQiWGSUOYTNQj6VCyiTfw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*JbjYXF7q-ZGKnGvpWOjWOg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>2. Los Especiales （老派churros攤，他們的churros真的是油條的味道不是吉拿棒。記得要沾砂糖不然偏鹹。巧克力味道馬力歐說很正宗，我覺得不太好喝，看情況加點）（地點很好就在河邊）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*Gxwq3uxswHG0NzvmfiMBag@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*W3MiYUvVD3sjjcbGPgKcxg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>3. Dulcería Manu Jara （老派甜點店，馬力歐覺得是塞維亞第一名（台灣人來說應該還是太甜，但可以嘗試）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*6fWOm8bIqxxNP7WohTkOsw@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>Press enter or click to view image in full size</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*nXt3zwGtrV726ktS6bmm6Q@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><h2><strong>市場/超市</strong></h2><p>1.Mercadona （東西齊全的西班牙連鎖超市，有非常厲害的起司、火雞臘腸、熟食區烘蛋也非常好吃) (我大推薦起司蛋糕，但不推薦flan）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*80hjLLXbVZMh5af8z2DRDg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="700" height="934"><p>2.Setas de Sevilla (有名的都市陽傘，樓下有市場，看似蕭條但生火腿超級好吃，老闆會請試吃，我吃了一片之後直接買一包）</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*US4arDCRP3cXCKmHGcT3fg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*EYpiYDeLC_q_XtEuLCQ5Bg@2x.jpeg" alt="" width="500" height="4032"><p>【同場加映】馬力歐呼籲觀光客不要在塞維亞做的事</p><ol><li><p>點sangria</p></li></ol><p>馬力歐說sangria是觀光客在喝的，當地人通常都喝啤酒。若想喝清涼感的類似飲品可以點tinto de veranó，這是加了氣泡水的紅酒，喝起來略帶甜味很清爽）</p><p>2. 用叉子吃生火腿</p><p>我跟馬力歐在市集買生火腿，他跟生火腿店老闆看到有觀光客點了生火腿跟他們要叉子，面面相覷一臉苦笑。生火腿對他們來說應該是用手拿來吃，手的溫度稍微融化油脂，附在手指上的油香也是美味的一部份</p><p>3. 吃paella</p><p>西班牙食物區域性很強，燉飯是加利西亞的名產不是安達魯西亞。想吃飯類在塞維亞還是有很多其他選擇。但是飯類最好還是吃現點現煮的，建議不要點飯類tapas因為那都不是現煮</p><p>4. 啤酒不要點1 pint</p><p>西班牙啤酒都是小容量的杯子，若看到酒吧有1 pint的大杯，那通常是賣觀光客。</p><p>＊馬力歐當地人意見僅供參考，我是覺得旅行的時候想吃什麼喝什麼都可以不用太拘泥。不過都來塞維亞了，多吃點當地特色食物也不錯喔。</p>	PUBLISHED	2025-08-11 14:11:49.317	2025-08-12 09:31:06.926	2	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*OU7j6jjwaq5IBl-Ee5SRKw.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 700, "height": 934}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "男友馬力歐來自西班牙塞維亞Sevilla, 我第一次來西班牙很幸運可以跟著他到處吃喝。這邊是他身為當地人拍胸脯保證的推薦，給大家去西班牙旅遊一個參考。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Bar (for tapas) 推薦酒吧（西班牙bar通常都有tapas, 可以想像成有賣酒的台灣小吃攤。若是餐廳就是比較正式會有服務生來點餐的地方）", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"type": null, "start": 1}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Cafetería-Bar Trinidad (宵夜場, 蝸牛好吃, 非常local) (招牌是豬肉片生火腿薯條三明治，記得加大蒜美乃滋）", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*kKQJHYnKEXwWwJ_pSJMC_w@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*NMTOoCIh_49sBDgYwDZw3Q@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Press enter or click to view image in full size", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*mDyntXuzUvJ3ZLXfsqx2-g@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "2. Bodega San Rafael （在市中心邊陲，但喜歡吃海鮮的人請一定要來。當地人才會去的海鮮酒吧，請點蟹腳、大蝦、小型粉紅蝦。老闆應該不會說英文，但海鮮都在櫃子裡可以直接用指的）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*nd8Vta6pmKtpxMwsIcG9Qg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*4L-9W-kVHaorgn1gJiTa9g@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*BcdaqMm7wpCUjzZUue4iXQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*dqPhxlD8YPjGrcPs9c0mWg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "3. Los Coloniales (市中心，推薦章魚、煎大蒜豬排配威士忌酒醬。東西好吃，氣氛比較不吵）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*B6ZMHlySLFCXYaXQp8LZtw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*cfhZ03MF3Pab8QyFDF0QqA@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*ewniT4BxBJmsj3hkubhieQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "4. El Rinconcillo （塞維亞最老酒吧，內裝非常好看值得去拍照。食物中規中矩，簡單吃生火腿跟起司喝杯酒就很好）（甜點菜單不錯可以多嘗試）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*p0byni__wzuHhS8JcHNJxA@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*k72ldGfKY3N_AJ6SbVcpOw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*RtttOTOFVYrmE4v1qQTW7A@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*Uk9bqtODZMZ1fBPjG-i4hw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*E88d8BOQaBbGU6Y9bnjzqg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "5. El Rey de los Caracoles （神秘蝸牛專賣小酒吧，裝潢簡約宗教系，只有當地阿伯會去。老闆幽默風趣）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*tP7ELrPm0y6RQMwkOk1spQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*dIfuvXvnn_P3gPd2zoeCHQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "6. Bar Paco Góngora （市中心，英文菜單友善，食物選擇多，但相較之下不是最好吃的）（我覺得墨魚飯不好吃，不建議點）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*a4y2uL_1aXxibFXmixALUA@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*Z6amvKg8yMxEVt1yG5P-qw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*8t5okGuZcmXRWFWaecgh1Q@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*0JwShuzEnDoAoUfsDRmsHQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "7. Bodega Santa Cruz （靠近大教堂，生意極好。草根系酒吧，有金山鵝肉的感覺。馬鈴薯沙拉好吃）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*9wwpkmuJkjzoh7zVFjVbEQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*zToNFkfzmOrh6xgXvt4USw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "*雷：Taberna Álvaro Peregil （在教堂附近那條街的食物大部分都賣觀光客，這間當地人也推薦但食物真的不好吃。酒類還是可以喝喝）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "早餐", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"type": null, "start": 1}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Bodega El Picadero （老派早餐店，西班牙永和豆漿，也有賣tapas。喜歡甜咖啡的人可以點coffee bom bom, 會直接給你一瓶煉乳讓你擠到飽）", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*oSXsWk3ZAweEUECJIW1m2A@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*SbjuaddVUfKOVIQdtXgP6g@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*ngqrATlKfa-wcBc2Y4a1AQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*qyDMK8bJIO54nuTTOcHniA@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "2. Bar Duque (早餐, 有圖片，有Churros,老派,市中心）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*gBvyZwlKBxyZlPnriWYD1Q@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*I-UPgaAsSzBaOUihak8TJg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "馬力歐老家 Montequinto (不在Seville市中心，方圓百里沒有觀光客，但食物真的比市中心好吃）", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"type": null, "start": 1}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Restaurante Burravieja （石板烤依比利豬肉片非常好吃又大盤/大蒜蛤蜊炒蝦很台超好吃啊啊啊）", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*zBiehhqd7L72LfE3dLv7Ig@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*rEEDuxdXhUFGinowKpkZSw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "2. Cervecería Un Poquito (戶外座位很熱鬧很local, 賽維亞賣最多種啤酒的地方。海鮮種類選擇多，熱菜也好吃。會用麥克風唱名去拿菜）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*2z8qUV9Or39Z-mIqkQx6pg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*5PuwEMoI0Mxo47Swn5qQgw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*tXOsZORIHfXo2m0fSXPBJg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 334, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*vDuNTNEizx0fs1HJWdE3pA@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*3VBzMyRG6gnN54XWJ-6ghQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "3. Los Caminantes （海鮮極美味又便宜。langoustine(cigala) 蝦腦極讚、各種蝦類都無敵）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*G0gXCxThMBIh3CaaqegZZQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*FaGncPeODYR6Pzb9EKmZAQ@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "特色酒吧（沒有食物）", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Bar Garlochí （極盡浮誇之宗教系酒吧，老闆非常妙。招牌調酒是“耶穌的寶血”。推薦去參觀佈置）（裡面有點非常濃的香，密閉龍山寺的概念，老闆自爆他有得肺癌）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*YhajgzzRGsUzcwDVDs1reA@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*cHu6nLFFs00pnvUFACpW3w@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*2ILiZf7JDmOzYW9eHjuWIg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:2160/1*_Ifo2ju0YoPbZ2hre_1jbA@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 1920}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "甜點", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"type": null, "start": 1}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Helados Rayas （塞維亞最有名冰淇淋店，有非常多西班牙特色口味）", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*BCQiWGSUOYTNQj6VCyiTfw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*JbjYXF7q-ZGKnGvpWOjWOg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "2. Los Especiales （老派churros攤，他們的churros真的是油條的味道不是吉拿棒。記得要沾砂糖不然偏鹹。巧克力味道馬力歐說很正宗，我覺得不太好喝，看情況加點）（地點很好就在河邊）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*Gxwq3uxswHG0NzvmfiMBag@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*W3MiYUvVD3sjjcbGPgKcxg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "3. Dulcería Manu Jara （老派甜點店，馬力歐覺得是塞維亞第一名（台灣人來說應該還是太甜，但可以嘗試）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*6fWOm8bIqxxNP7WohTkOsw@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Press enter or click to view image in full size", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*nXt3zwGtrV726ktS6bmm6Q@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "市場/超市", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "1.Mercadona （東西齊全的西班牙連鎖超市，有非常厲害的起司、火雞臘腸、熟食區烘蛋也非常好吃) (我大推薦起司蛋糕，但不推薦flan）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*80hjLLXbVZMh5af8z2DRDg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 700, "height": 934}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "2.Setas de Sevilla (有名的都市陽傘，樓下有市場，看似蕭條但生火腿超級好吃，老闆會請試吃，我吃了一片之後直接買一包）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*US4arDCRP3cXCKmHGcT3fg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": "", "src": "https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:6048/1*EYpiYDeLC_q_XtEuLCQ5Bg@2x.jpeg", "title": null, "width": 500, "height": 4032}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "【同場加映】馬力歐呼籲觀光客不要在塞維亞做的事", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"type": null, "start": 1}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "點sangria", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "馬力歐說sangria是觀光客在喝的，當地人通常都喝啤酒。若想喝清涼感的類似飲品可以點tinto de veranó，這是加了氣泡水的紅酒，喝起來略帶甜味很清爽）", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "2. 用叉子吃生火腿", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "我跟馬力歐在市集買生火腿，他跟生火腿店老闆看到有觀光客點了生火腿跟他們要叉子，面面相覷一臉苦笑。生火腿對他們來說應該是用手拿來吃，手的溫度稍微融化油脂，附在手指上的油香也是美味的一部份", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "3. 吃paella", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "西班牙食物區域性很強，燉飯是加利西亞的名產不是安達魯西亞。想吃飯類在塞維亞還是有很多其他選擇。但是飯類最好還是吃現點現煮的，建議不要點飯類tapas因為那都不是現煮", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "4. 啤酒不要點1 pint", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "西班牙啤酒都是小容量的杯子，若看到酒吧有1 pint的大杯，那通常是賣觀光客。", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "＊馬力歐當地人意見僅供參考，我是覺得旅行的時候想吃什麼喝什麼都可以不用太拘泥。不過都來塞維亞了，多吃點當地特色食物也不錯喔。", "type": "text"}]}]}	http://localhost:8081/uploads/cover-image/1754921502308-507701289.jpg
25	1	【一日登山：Setia Alam Community Trail】追著流行的風	<p>如果要點名時下一座流行的「網紅山」，那麼這非Setia Alam Community Trail莫屬了。從結束MCO至今，有關它的打卡照一直輪流出現在每個山友的臉書相冊。於是趁著空閒的週末，約上數月不見的Vivian，一起追著流行的風來到了這座「網紅山」。</p><p>這座「網紅山」其實是市區森林步道，座落在Shah Alam Community Forest (SACF)裡。這座森林猶如這市區的綠肺，四周都是黃金發展地段，而它是唯一被守護下來的一塊綠區，一直深受大自然愛好者的喜愛。即使早上下著綿綿細雨，卻也毫無影響綠區內的人氣。</p><p>由於我和Vivian都是新来乍到，對於綠區內多條登山步道一無所知。於是出發前我下載了其中一條登山環線圖 — <a target="_blank" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" class="bg zj" href="https://www.alltrails.com/explore/recording/afternoon-hike-b80ba73--9?u=m"><u>Setia Alam and Sapu Tangan Loop</u></a>，然後隨性的跟著大眾的腳印游走在森林裡，朝聖了隱藏在這裡最熱門的打卡地點：Peak Garden, Mirror Lake, Sapu Tangan Lookout Tower 。</p><p>Press enter or click to view image in full size</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*wEcppuhVzF12cUPUyIoIgA.jpeg" alt="" width="700" height="394"><p>Tasik Rimba Bayu Lake (Mirror Lake)</p><p>首先是Peak Garden，這裡能高處欣賞在雲海之下的城市全景，但其實當天我們對這幅風景毫無知情而完美與它擦肩而过。</p><p>接著我們來到了隱藏在這座綠色森林中的藍色湖泊，原名為Tasik Rimba Bayu Lake。因為那裡寧靜的湖面將湖中那高高低低的枯木勾勒出更優美的倒影畫面，造就了「鏡湖-Mirror Lake」的名稱。這天剛好遇上了雨後微风吹走了湖面平靜，水面上蕩起陣陣漣漪反映了湖岸上的人潮，也讓我巧遇了在Gunung Tok Nenek一起野營的山友們。</p><p>最後一站就是Bukit Sapu Tangan山頂上的Lookout Tower。可惜這座高木塔遇上白蟻嚴重破壞而遭封塔，所以人人只能在塔下打卡，並不知道塔上的風景如何。</p><p>Press enter or click to view image in full size</p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/1*H141ut443s45gGf9zBq9rQ.jpeg" alt="" width="700" height="395"><p>Sapu Tangan Lookout Tower</p><p>打卡只是一個目的，真正讓我享受的是和Vivian兩人在路上悠哉的步伐。不急著打卡，不緩著聊天，全程花了七小時來結束這條登山環線（原本只需花少於五小時）。或許MCO為我們添上了不少話題，看著Vivian也開始為自己紀錄路上的印記，於是我們不小心聊出了「興趣」。</p><blockquote><p>興趣是你生活中美麗的養分。能找到一份自己喜歡做的事情，即使再累也值得你開心。</p></blockquote><p>因為短期的行動受限，點醒了自己最愛做的事情是什麼，了解了「興趣」在生活中扮演了不可或缺的角色。它是養分，它是寄託，它的印記提亮了暗沈的生活。可惜過去有許多的美好回憶早已經被時間沖得模糊不清，尤其我這顆金魚腦袋更本裝不下任何細節。於是MCO之後，才讓我決定打開這一個空間來好好存放在山林與我的印記，透過紀錄來更了解我所爬過的每一座山，學習去當這興趣的紀錄者。</p>	PUBLISHED	2025-08-11 14:13:30.507	2025-08-12 09:31:06.926	4	{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "如果要點名時下一座流行的「網紅山」，那麼這非Setia Alam Commun